text: Jeram is a mukim in Kuala Selangor District, Selangor, Malaysia. Jeram may also refer to: * Jeram, California, former settlement in Mendocino County * Jeram (state constituency), in Selangor, Malaysia * Anita Jeram (born 1965), English author and illustrator of picture books * Praven Jeram (fl. 1971–1977), New Zealand football goalkeeper
